WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:00.971
Good morning, family.

00:00:00.971 --> 00:00:03.404
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:03.404 --> 00:00:04.649
I have a word.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:19.689
You know, I usually come on here and have a lot of negative words—what people would call doom and gloom.

00:00:19.689 --> 00:00:50.260
But today, I have the opportunity to give you a positive word, an uplifting word, an encouraging word that people have been believing for decades and decades, maybe thousands of years.

00:00:50.260 --> 00:01:03.879
You know, cancer has been around for a long, long time.

00:01:21.426 --> 00:01:24.319
The Lord spoke to me whenever I was praying, and He opened my eyes in the realm of the spirit.

00:01:26.799 --> 00:01:32.360
He said, "Brandon, I'm bringing the cure for cancer.

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:46.874
" I saw a man in a lab coat, and he was pouring some stuff in a jar.

00:01:46.874 --> 00:02:11.017
All of a sudden, Holy Ghost revelation came to his mind, and he saw it—whatever it was, I don't know, I'm not a chemist.

00:02:11.017 --> 00:02:24.874
He put it together, then he looked at it underneath the microscope and found it by the Holy Spirit.

00:02:40.707 --> 00:02:41.156
The Lord spoke to me and said this man is not even a born-again Christian.

00:02:42.502 --> 00:03:03.440
He warned me and said, "Brandon, I'm bringing this to pass because people have cried out to Me for a long time.

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:15.335
They have been believing for their relatives and people that have gone home too early.

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:30.280
" This has been a plague on humanity, and the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm bringing a cure for this.

00:03:31.834 --> 00:04:07.995
" He said, "I'm going to put My foot on this, and it will become like plagues of the past that were completely eradicated, things we don't hear about anymore, like leprosy or tuberculosis—things that were very deadly in the early 1800s before they came out with the vaccinations.

00:04:07.995 --> 00:04:26.371
" Some of those viruses back then were very serious, but now, with antibiotics, it's able to be taken care of a lot easier.

00:04:36.044 --> 00:04:40.531
The Lord told me this will be a preventative and a cure at the same time.

00:04:44.085 --> 00:05:05.243
He said people can take this and will never even have it in their body, and the people that have it will automatically be healed; it will just leave them.

00:05:05.626 --> 00:05:21.180
The way He presented it to me was that it didn't matter what kind of cancer it was, it would be gone.

00:05:21.180 --> 00:05:34.084
It wouldn't be a long, drawn-out process; it would just instantaneously start to turn the ship around.

00:05:36.875 --> 00:05:44.290
The Lord said to me it would not be a medication; it would be like a supplement.

00:05:44.290 --> 00:05:49.360
That's how simple He said it is.

00:05:55.573 --> 00:05:57.440
He said, "Son, it's something so simple coming from the earth.

00:05:57.440 --> 00:06:08.990
" Whenever they put these things together, it will create the combination that it takes for the cure.

00:06:08.990 --> 00:06:16.400
It's designed perfectly for it, but it's divine from God.

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:18.830
Does that make sense?

00:06:19.948 --> 00:06:42.160
I'm doing the best I can with this, but what I saw in the spirit was the Lord telling me that cancer would become a thing of the past.

00:06:42.160 --> 00:07:13.520
There would be government things that would rise up to try to stop it, but the Lord would put His hand on it to stop them because He said this has been something that has been dealt with for too long.

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:24.950
I was so filled with the Holy Spirit whenever He gave me this word.

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:42.599
I couldn't wait to come on here and tell you what the Lord is telling me is coming for the world.

00:07:42.599 --> 00:08:04.062
It's because God so loved the world that He gave His one and only begotten son, that whosoever believes in Him should not perish but have everlasting life.

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:13.213
He gave salvation to everybody.

00:08:13.213 --> 00:08:22.280
That's the way God is—He's not just about Christians; He's about loving everybody.

00:08:31.061 --> 00:08:34.262
He wants everybody to come to repentance so they don't have to go to hell.

00:08:34.262 --> 00:08:36.298
Bottom line, folks.

00:08:36.298 --> 00:08:44.422
He's not up there with a big stick hitting people in the head.

00:08:44.422 --> 00:08:51.783
He wants to show you His love and His kindness.

00:09:06.222 --> 00:09:13.920
He gave His son, who died for us and rose again on the third day, and He is seated right now at the right hand of the Father.

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:29.049
I'm telling you, He's coming back again, but He has a present for all of us.

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:43.640
Jesus took all those things on the cross for us; we don't have to have it now.

00:09:43.640 --> 00:09:59.399
But some people don't have the faith to believe for healing, or the cure for cancer, or diabetes.

00:09:59.399 --> 00:10:07.840
Jesus paid the price for everybody to have health and healing.

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:24.830
Sometimes He uses medicine to help folks that don't know how to believe by faith, and that's just the mercy of God.

00:10:24.830 --> 00:10:41.874
What I'm trying to tell you is that He told me He is giving a supernatural wisdom to this man that was mixing stuff.

00:10:45.430 --> 00:10:50.862
I saw the company name and where it was located.

00:10:50.862 --> 00:11:01.143
I'm praying over it still; you can pray with me.

00:11:01.143 --> 00:11:17.489
I'm not going to give that out yet because I don't want any demonic attacks trying to come against this.

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:30.267
I believe God is going to do what He said He would do.

00:11:35.065 --> 00:11:35.420
The company does exist.

00:11:43.365 --> 00:11:51.584
They are working with supplements right now, but I don't even know if they know about it yet.

00:11:51.584 --> 00:12:04.560
I see things in part and hear in part, sometimes years in advance.

00:12:04.560 --> 00:12:19.034
There have been times whenever He has told me to pray for companies that didn't even exist yet.

00:12:19.034 --> 00:12:27.880
He'll give me a name and spell it out in a vision.

00:12:27.880 --> 00:12:47.352
I'll try to Google it, and it doesn't exist yet, but He says, "I want you to intercede for this name.

00:12:57.848 --> 00:13:02.114
" So I pray over the name for months or years.

00:13:02.114 --> 00:13:10.782
All of a sudden, He'll say, "Brandon, that company has been birthed and it is existing now.

00:13:19.760 --> 00:13:20.119
I want you to go Google it," and it's there.

00:13:20.119 --> 00:13:31.447
